    {
        "content": "<p>Looking forward to see you all in Leuven in 2027. <span aria-label=\"tada\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f389\" role=\"img\" title=\"tada\">:tada:</span></p>",
        "id": 595300608,
        "sender_full_name": "Oliver Bertuch",
        "timestamp": 1778850192
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>We look forward to seeing you all there!<br>\n<img alt=\"DCM2027 stil.png\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"1920x1080\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/53090/Ho6mqdUviN-bkw4htTdcdpnY/DCM2027-stil.png\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/53090/Ho6mqdUviN-bkw4htTdcdpnY/DCM2027-stil.png/840x560.webp\"></p>",
        "id": 595358226,
        "sender_full_name": "Dieuwertje Bloemen",
        "timestamp": 1778865889
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It's not completely unreasonable to do this by bike.<br>\n<img alt=\"image.png\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"1877x757\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/53090/rf1maCNmEKpAP0FvR8bhJG3A/image.png\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/53090/rf1maCNmEKpAP0FvR8bhJG3A/image.png/840x560.webp\"></p>",
        "id": 595389552,
        "sender_full_name": "Oliver Bertuch",
        "timestamp": 1778875903
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Here's the announcement <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"660583\">@Dieuwertje Bloemen</span> posted to the mailing list: <a href=\"https://groups.google.com/g/dataverse-community/c/TLl0FIcZqRI/m/1A9JdMkzAgAJ\">https://groups.google.com/g/dataverse-community/c/TLl0FIcZqRI/m/1A9JdMkzAgAJ</a></p>\n<p>Exciting! <span aria-label=\"tada\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f389\" role=\"img\" title=\"tada\">:tada:</span> <span aria-label=\"flag belgium\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f1e7-1f1ea\" role=\"img\" title=\"flag belgium\">:flag_belgium:</span> <img alt=\":dataverse:\" class=\"emoji\" src=\"https://avatars.zulip.com/53090/emoji/images/e48ac253.png\" title=\"dataverse\"></p>",
        "id": 596532444,
        "sender_full_name": "Philip Durbin 🚀",
        "timestamp": 1779301372
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I went ahead and <a href=\"https://calendar.google.com/calendar/u/0/event?eid=NjRrY2MyOHVqcW5lbjI5M2RhcTcxNjZudnAgY191ZG40dG9ubTQwMWtnampyZTRqbDRqYTBjc0Bn\">added it</a> to the community calendar.</p>",
        "id": 596533391,
        "sender_full_name": "Philip Durbin 🚀",
        "timestamp": 1779301647
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I just updated the banner at <a href=\"http://dataverse.org\">dataverse.org</a> to match what we have at <a href=\"http://gdcc.io\">gdcc.io</a> (thanks <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"660583\">@Dieuwertje Bloemen</span> for updating that!):</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2026-07-08 at 10.54.39 AM.png\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"745x284\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/53090/zIJtYfOXaFb8W51ccR_VqFvZ/Screenshot-2026-07-08-at-10.54.39AM.png\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/53090/zIJtYfOXaFb8W51ccR_VqFvZ/Screenshot-2026-07-08-at-10.54.39AM.png/840x560.webp\"></p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2026-07-08 at 10.55.47 AM.png\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"778x88\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/53090/8R51NkWagfF4T96BPPJxzhrK/Screenshot-2026-07-08-at-10.55.47AM.png\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/53090/8R51NkWagfF4T96BPPJxzhrK/Screenshot-2026-07-08-at-10.55.47AM.png/840x560.webp\"></p>\n<p>I also updated <a href=\"https://dataverse.org/events\">https://dataverse.org/events</a> to mention the 2027 meeting.</p>\n<p>In all cases, I'm linking back to this topic in Zulip but when there is a web page ready for the 2027 DCM, please ping me and we can update all of the above!</p>",
